Just see what happens.

33
00:08:45.727 --> 00:08:48.063
When I report to Beijing,

34
00:08:48.147 --> 00:08:52.151
the chief and the new boss Jiao
will be hauling sand in prison.


35
00:08:52.234 --> 00:08:56.530
Before you even get to Taiyuan,
the chief's men will catch you.


36
00:08:56.613 --> 00:08:59.616
Why do you think I studied law?

37
00:08:59.700 --> 00:09:02.995
The chief sold off
collectively owned property.


38
00:09:03.078 --> 00:09:05.122
He accepted a bribe.

39
00:09:05.205 --> 00:09:07.166
