40
00:09:07.249 --> 00:09:10.961
As for your boss Jiao Shengli,
he's rolling in it, right?


41
00:09:11.044 --> 00:09:14.590
<i>I'll</i> accuse him of polluting
and covering up accidents in the mine.


42
00:09:14.673 --> 00:09:16.258
They'll close him down.

43
00:09:16.341 --> 00:09:18.760
Believe it.

44
00:09:19.761 --> 00:09:25.601
If the coal mine had gone to you,
you'd have been no different.


45
00:09:25.684 --> 00:09:27.561
I would have.

46
00:09:27.644 --> 00:09:32.232
