49
00:09:41.116 --> 00:09:44.661
- Sanming. Got the train ticket?
- Yes.


50
00:09:44.745 --> 00:09:47.915
- Where are you going?
- To see my wife for New Year's.


51
00:09:47.998 --> 00:09:50.083
That's romantic.

52
00:09:51.168 --> 00:09:53.170
The police are here.

53
00:09:53.253 --> 00:09:55.088
Stop eating.

54
00:09:57.674 --> 00:09:59.510
Investigation.

55
00:09:59.593 --> 00:10:02.179
Are all the migrant workers here?

56
00:10:02.262 --> 00:10:03.597
Yes. What's wrong?

57
00:10:03.680 --> 00:10:07.017
A murder in Shibawan.
The migrants have to be checked.


58
00:10:07.100 --> 00:10:10.187
Get them all outside.

59
00:10:10.270 --> 00:10:11.980
Hurry!

60
00:10:19.029 --> 00:10:20.322
Chief.

61
00:10:20.405 --> 00:10:21.532
Village Chief.

62
00:10:21.615 --> 00:10:25.661
When you sold off the coal mine
you promised yearly dividends.


63
00:10:25.744 --> 00:10:27.704
I said that in private.

64
00:10:27.788 --> 00:10:29.623
I don't have time now.

65
00:10:29.706 --> 00:10:33.085
Okay, explain it
to the Discipline Commission.


66
00:10:37.631 --> 00:10:41.635
You've picked
the wrong time for a fight.


67
00:10:42.553 --> 00:10:45.347
You'll be a loser your whole life.

68
00:10:57.901 --> 00:11:01.530
- You won't discuss it?
- You talk too much.


69
00:11:10.497 --> 00:11:14.042
Okay. People from Chongqing.

70
00:11:32.477 --> 00:11:33.687
Over there.

71
00:11:33.770 --> 00:11:35.022
Next.

72
00:11:56.376 --> 00:11:58.253
He's making a run for it!

73
00:12:19.274 --> 00:12:20.776
Damn animal!

74
00:13:08.031 --> 00:13:09.074
<i>What' s up, Baha'i?</i>

75
00:13:09.157 --> 00:13:11.993
I'm writing to the Discipline Commission

76
00:13:12.077 --> 00:13:15.205
to complain about the chief
and Jiao Shengli.


77
00:13:16.123 --> 00:13:18.625
Miss, a registered letter.

78
00:13:18.709 --> 00:13:22.587
- To whom?
- Beijing. Zhongnanhai. The Commission.


79
00:13:22.671 --> 00:13:25.382
I need the full address.

80
00:13:25.465 --> 00:13:27.300
Zhongnanhai, Beijing.

81
00:13:27.384 --> 00:13:30.595
That's not enough. 
I need the full address.

82
00:13:30.679 --> 00:13:33.974
What? Everyone knows Zhongnanhai.

83
00:13:34.057 --> 00:13:36.059
That's not enough.

84
00:13:36.143 --> 00:13:39.020
Miss, are you siding
with the village chief?


85
00:13:39.104 --> 00:13:41.440
Does he give you kickbacks?

86
00:13:41.523 --> 00:13:45.527
Or are you Jiao's mistress?
Has he bought you a car?


87
00:13:45.610 --> 00:13:47.654
You're crazy! Go away!

88
00:13:48.447 --> 00:13:50.907
You two must be in league.

89
00:13:50.991 --> 00:13:52.868
There's no justice!

90
