All aboard! We're leaving, hurry!

93
00:14:11.178 --> 00:14:14.014
Dahai, come on!

94
00:14:15.474 --> 00:14:16.558
What's this for?

95
00:14:16.641 --> 00:14:20.729
Greeting Boss Jiao.
One bag of flour per person.


96
00:14:26.485 --> 00:14:30.405
Boss Jiao has a new private plane.
He's flying back from Hong Kong.


97
00:14:30.489 --> 00:14:33.825
We're a welcoming group.
Everyone gets a bag of flour.


98
00:14:33.909 --> 00:14:37.287
A plane?
Living on this earth isn't enough?


99
00:14:41.875 --> 00:14:44.628
Were you at the coal mine
when the gun was fired?


100
00:14:44.711 --> 00:14:46.254
Yes.

101
00:14:47.088 --> 00:14:49.216
Who was the guy who ran away?

102
00:14:49.299 --> 00:14:52.844
A loader in the coal yard. From Sichuan.

103
00:14:52.928 --> 00:14:56.598
Why did he run? 
The killings in Shibawan?

104
00:14:56.681 --> 00:14:58.850
He's an escaped prisoner.

105
00:14:58.934 --> 00:15:02.062
Killed someone in his hometown.
He's been hiding here.


106
00:15:02.145 --> 00:15:03.980
He thought they'd come for him.

107
00:15:04.064 --> 00:15:06.483
He panicked and ran.

108
00:15:06.566 --> 00:15:10.028
- Did they catch him?
- Of course.


109
00:15:13.240 --> 00:15:16.117
- What happened in Shibawan?
- Don't you know?


110
00:15:16.201 --> 00:15:20.872
Someone shot three guys yesterday.
Three dead in Shibawan.


111
00:15:20.956 --> 00:15:23.500
- Who did it?
- I don't know.


112
00:15:23.583 --> 00:15:28.421
Early this morning,
a bunch of armed police were in Shibawan.


113
00:15:29.256 --> 00:15:31.424
I see.

114
00:15:34.678 --> 00:15:38.265
Accountant Liu,
are your accounts up to date?


115
00:15:40.016 --> 00:15:44.062
When Boss Jiao got
hold of the coal mine

116
00:15:44.145 --> 00:15:47.649
he said 40% of the profits
would go to the village.


117
00:15:47.732 --> 00:15:52.320
How much do the last

118
00:15:52.404 --> 00:15:55.448
Listen, back in 2001,

119
00:15:55.532 --> 00:15:59.077
the village committee
signed to sell the coal mine.


120
00:15:59.160 --> 00:16:01.162
Who asked you to sell it?

121
00:16:01.246 --> 00:16:03.498
Was the contract discussed?

122
00:16:03.582 --> 00:16:05.834
We must keep our word.

123
00:16:05.917 --> 00:16:10.881
But Jiao got so rich
he even bought a plane.


124
00:16:10.964 --> 00:16:13.008
He's a hard worker.

125
00:16:13.091 --> 00:16:19.222
Then tell me how much you
and the chief took in bribes.


126
00:16:19.306 --> 00:16:21.474
Stop, please.

127
00:16:23.143 --> 00:16:26.062
Tell me how much you took in bribes.

128
00:16:26.146 --> 00:16:27.689
Open the door.

129
00:16:27.772 --> 00:16:32.444
Devils like you are more evil
than the village chief and Jiao.


130
00:16:38.825 --> 00:16:42.495
- Listen to me -
- Don't talk to me.


131
00:16:51.171 --> 00:16:54.090
Everyone, repeat after me.

132
00:16:54.507 --> 00:16:55.592
Welcome! Welcome!

133
00:16:55.675 --> 00:16:57.218
A warm welcome!

134
00:17:00.555 --> 00:17:01.973
Good.

135
00:17:03.141 --> 00:17:05.101
Here's the plane!

136
00:18:02.575 --> 00:18:05.662
Mr. Jiao, you've reached a new level.

137
00:18:05.745 --> 00:18:08.415
Let's progress together.

138
00:18:08.498 --> 00:18:10.750
Congratulations, ma'am.

139
00:18:10.834 --> 00:18:12.585
Kids, the flowers.

140
00:18:21.720 --> 00:18:23.972
Mr. Jiao, look this way.

141
00:18:26.599 --> 00:18:29.019
A bit closer, please.

142
00:18:29.936 --> 00:18:33.273
- Please say something, sir.
- Later.


143
00:18:44.951 --> 00:18:46.953
How are you, Auntie?

144
00:18:50.915 --> 00:18:52.709
Thanks for coming.

145
00:18:52.792 --> 00:18:54.711
Long time no see.

146
00:18:54.794 --> 00:18:57.380
- Shengli!
- Dahai.


147
00:18:57.464 --> 00:18:59.549
Congratulations.

148
00:18:59.632 --> 00:19:01.551
Thank you, Dahai.

149
00:19:01.634 --> 00:19:03.762
You're a hard man to reach.

150
00:19:03.845 --> 00:19:05.889
There's something I want to discuss.

151
00:19:05.972 --> 00:19:07.932
Can you do me a favor?

152
00:19:08.016 --> 00:19:09.934
Whatever you need, just ask.

153
00:19:10.018 --> 00:19:11.853
Sponsor my journey to Beijing

154
00:19:11.936 --> 00:19:15.356
to file accusations
against you and the village chief.


155
00:19:15.857 --> 00:19:18.651
Sure, come and pick it up later.

156
00:19:18.735 --> 00:19:21.112
Here, in front of all these villagers,

157
00:19:21.196 --> 00:19:24.365
can't you discuss the village economy?

158
00:19:28.036 --> 00:19:30.330
What are you staring at?

159
00:20:09.369 --> 00:20:12.580
Xiao Bai, are you playing golf?

160
00:20:44.571 --> 00:20:48.408
I'm hereto compensate you
on behalf of the Shengli Group.


161
00:21:08.595 --> 00:21:10.430
Case closed.

162
00:22:51.406 --> 00:22:53.116
Where's your mother?

163
00:22:53.199 --> 00:22:56.786
- Who are you?
- Don't you remember me?


164
00:22:56.869 --> 00:23:00.623
I'm your uncle from Wujinshan.

165
00:23:00.707 --> 00:23:04.127
Morn went out for food.
She'll be back soon.


166
00:23:09.549 --> 00:23:12.218
Animal.

167
00:23:15.305 --> 00:23:17.265
Where's your dad?

168
00:23:17.348 --> 00:23:20.601
Out hunting “animals.”

169
00:23:20.685 --> 00:23:22.770
On which mountain?

170
00:23:22.854 --> 00:23:24.564
Jiaokou.

171
00:23:26.774 --> 00:23:28.526
Dahai

172
00:23:29.235 --> 00:23:30.570
You've -

173
00:23:32.071 --> 00:23:34.240
When did you get here?

174
00:23:34.324 --> 00:23:36.993
I've been in town a couple of days.

175
00:23:37.618 --> 00:23:39.579
Let's go inside.

176
00:23:40.121 --> 00:23:42.790
Ganggang. Eat first, then homework.

177
00:23:42.874 --> 00:23:44.876
Of course, Mom.

178
00:23:45.835 --> 00:23:47.712
You're -

179
00:23:49.630 --> 00:23:51.257
Tell me.

180
00:23:55.345 --> 00:23:59.057
A while back,
I introduced you to a woman from Wangcun.


181
00:23:59.140 --> 00:24:01.184
You were well matched.

182
00:24:01.267 --> 00:24:02.477
But you -

183
00:24:02.560 --> 00:24:05.646
Why didn't you date her, as arranged?

184
00:24:05.730 --> 00:24:09.817
You never think about your life.

185
00:24:12.612 --> 00:24:14.989
All you do is make accusations.

186
00:24:15.073 --> 00:24:18.743
Even if your charges stick, you'll grow old.

187
00:24:18.826 --> 00:24:22.663
I'm already old. 
But I don't care.

188
00:24:22.747 --> 00:24:24.540
Don't be silly.

189
00:24:24.624 --> 00:24:27.293
You're only middle-aged.

190
00:24:32.465 --> 00:24:34.842
The kid's here.

191
00:24:36.928 --> 00:24:39.180
I'm at fault here.

192
00:24:39.263 --> 00:24:41.391
You really are hopeless.

193
00:24:41.474 --> 00:24:44.435
I told you when
we were still at school.

194
00:24:44.519 --> 00:24:47.230
There's more to life than getting rich.

195
00:24:47.313 --> 00:24:50.900
You want to be more evil
than Jiao Shengli?


196
00:24:50.983 --> 00:24:53.236
How can you compare me with him?

197
00:24:53.319 --> 00:24:55.488
If not him, then who?

198
00:24:55.571 --> 00:24:57.740
You and he were classmates.

199
00:24:57.824 --> 00:25:02.328
Look what he's made of himself
compared to us here.


200
00:25:02.995 --> 00:25:07.625
You have your own place in Wujinshan.

201
00:25:07.708 --> 00:25:13.589
But my husband and I
don't even have a home of our own.


202
00:25:15.466 --> 00:25:16.926
Enough of this.

203
00:25:17.009 --> 00:25:20.346
If you have time on your hands,
why not open a restaurant?


204
00:25:20.430 --> 00:25:23.641
Or a shop?
To earn money and get married.


205
00:25:23.724 --> 00:25:28.020
Your life belongs to you.
Stop caring what others do.


206
00:25:31.774 --> 00:25:34.735
My dear, wait and see.

207
00:25:34.819 --> 00:25:39.407
I can be more evil
than the village chief or Jiao.


208
00:26:09.979 --> 00:26:11.898
Isn't that Mr. Golf?

209
00:26:14.400 --> 00:26:16.611
- What did you call me?
- Mr. Golf.


210
00:26:16.694 --> 00:26:20.156
Everyone calls you Mr. Golf now.
Didn't you know?


211
00:26:39.675 --> 00:26:41.260
Mr. Golf!

212
00:26:56.025 --> 00:26:57.568
I...

213
00:27:00.029 --> 00:27:01.364
Lin Chong...

214
00:27:04.909 --> 00:27:08.412
unsheathed my sword and, in anger,

215
00:27:08.496 --> 00:27:11.332
slew two of Gao Qiu's henchmen.

216
00:27:11.415 --> 00:27:13.918
Fortunately for me,

217
00:27:14.001 --> 00:27:16.546
Officer Chai gave me a document

218
00:27:16.629 --> 00:27:20.716
which enabled me to come to Mount Liang.

219
00:29:29.929 --> 00:29:31.681
Good morning.

220
00:29:32.306 --> 00:29:33.599
Dahai, good morning.

221
00:29:33.683 --> 00:29:35.726
I want a word with your husband.

222
00:29:35.810 --> 00:29:37.645
Go ahead.

223
00:29:48.364 --> 00:29:49.907
Write.

224
00:29:53.536 --> 00:29:55.287
Write what?

225
00:29:57.957 --> 00:30:01.168
You know how much
the village chief embezzled.


226
00:30:01.252 --> 00:30:04.630
- Write a confession.
- You're being ridiculous.


227
00:30:13.305 --> 00:30:15.850
What are you doing? 
That's dangerous.

228
00:30:16.892 --> 00:30:18.728
Write it down.

229
00:30:21.647 --> 00:30:23.315
Write!

230
00:30:33.951 --> 00:30:35.327
Write.

231
00:31:00.352 --> 00:31:01.729
Shoot

232
00:31:04.023 --> 00:31:05.608
Shoot me here.

233
00:31:19.246 --> 00:31:22.166
You're too much of
a coward to kill me.

234
00:32:53.007 --> 00:32:56.093
Village Chief. it's Liuliu.

235
00:32:56.176 --> 00:32:58.137
I just started work.

236
00:32:59.638 --> 00:33:01.807
What do you want done?

237
00:33:03.976 --> 00:33:07.271
Okay, don't worry.
<i>I'll</i> do it this afternoon.


238
00:33:08.397 --> 00:33:10.149
Mr. Golf.

239
00:33:10.232 --> 00:33:12.401
- Where's the chief?
- At the temple.


240
00:33:15.446 --> 00:33:18.490
What did you just call me?

241
00:33:18.949 --> 00:33:20.242
Mr. Golf.

242
00:33:20.326 --> 00:33:22.995
Isn't that your foreign name?

243
00:33:23.078 --> 00:33:24.747
Little bastard.

244
00:33:24.830 --> 00:33:26.498
What did you say?

245
00:33:54.360 --> 00:33:56.236
- Dahai.
- Where are you off to?


246
00:33:56.320 --> 00:33:59.990
Fengjie. Going hunting?

247
00:34:00.074 --> 00:34:01.825
Hunting animals.

248
00:34:22.805 --> 00:34:24.890
Stop fooling around.

249
00:34:34.400 --> 00:34:36.235
Calm down.

250
00:34:37.486 --> 00:34:40.572
Let's sit down and talk.

251
00:34:41.073 --> 00:34:42.866
We can sort it out.

252
00:35:01.260 --> 00:35:04.680
Listen, don't be impulsive.

253
00:35:14.940 --> 00:35:16.442
Let's sit down.

254
00:36:01.320 --> 00:36:02.946
Bastard!

255
00:37:29.449 --> 00:37:31.201
Dahai?

256
00:37:44.882 --> 00:37:46.884
How can we fix this?

257
00:37:46.967 --> 00:37:48.135
Just tell me.

258
00:39:49.256 --> 00:39:50.716
Hey.

259
00:39:52.384 --> 00:39:54.678
You got a light?

260
00:39:54.761 --> 00:39:56.221
No.

261
00:40:12.070 --> 00:40:14.072
Motorcycle taxi.

262
00:40:27.919 --> 00:40:30.339
- Where to, buddy?
- The expressway.


263
00:40:30.422 --> 00:40:32.341
Let's go.

264
00:40:57.574 --> 00:41:02.329
<i>Our Mrs. Zhou here
worked hard to raise her children.</i>


265
